<html><head><title>Player Debate: Mythicals</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>Player Debate: Mythicals</h3><p>The hot debate this week seems to be, "Should mythical weapons be only for those who can join and contribute to a raiding guild?"<br><br>Some might say, yes, because there should be elite rewards for those people who put the time and effort into playing the hard core raiding game.  And if you aren't playing in the end game content, why do you need one?<br><br>Some say, no, everyone that plays should have a chance to get a mythical weapon, not just a select few that have more time to raid.<br><br>Where do you stand?<br><br>Read the player arguments pro and con for <a href="http://forums.station.sony.com/eq2/posts/list.m?topic_id=431449">mythical weapons</a> on the SOE boards.</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Tuesday, 21 Oct, 2008<br>Link: <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=46466">http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=46466</a><br>Printed On: Sat Aug 25 8:42:26 PDT 2012<br>©2008 IGN Entertainment</font></span>